| **Nominal Market Cap** | 8.49B × $0.0926 | **$786M** |
| **Float Market Cap** (ex-DAT, ex-sENA) | ~6.79B × $0.0926 | **$629M** |
| **Adjusted Market Cap** (ex-locked, ex-treasury) | ~8.49B × $0.0926 | **$786M** |
| **Fully Diluted Valuation (FDV)** | 15B × $0.0926 | **$1.39B** |
| **FDV / Float MCAP Ratio** | $1.39B / $786M | **1.77x** |

