| **TBD / Locked (Unallocated)** | 2,023,437,500 | 13.5% | Designation unclear |
| **DAT Holdings (Buybacks)** | ~779,890,000 | 5.2% | Held by Foundation; removed from float |
| **sENA (Staked)** | ~920,000,000 | 6.1% | Liquid but locked with 7-day cooldown |
| **Total Supply** | 15,000,000,000 | 100% | Max supply, no inflation |

### Market Cap Calculations

